#包装成函数
mean_c <- function(x){
    mean_x <- mean(x)
    i <- 1;
    length(x)
    for(i in 1:length(x)){
        if(x[i] > mean_x){
            x[i] = x[i] / 2
        } else if(x[i] < mean_x){
            x[i] = x[i] * 2
        }
    }
    x
}

#x平方，取对数/x+1, 最后开三次方
#中心极限定律

k <- NA
for(i in 1:1000000){
    y <- runif(10,min = 5,max = 15) #uniform distribution 均匀分布
    #rchisq(15,8)
    y <- y^2
    y <- log(y)/(y+1)
    y <- y^3
    mean_y <- mean(y)
    k[i] <- mean_y
}
hist(k,prob=T,col="light blue")
lines(density(k),col="red",lwd=3)
